Bare Composer Repository


Add Following to app's composer.json
======================================================================

"autoload": {
    "psr-4": {
        "Bare\" : "vendor/BricksIO/Bare/"
    }
}





Test if package installed correctly
======================================================================
//Run composer autoload
require "../vendor/autoload.php";


//Check if Package loaded correctly
$app = new Bare\Core\Application();
$app->run()
